snippet.title: Battle Chef Brigade Deluxe Edition | Announcement Trailer | PS4, Switch, and Steam
snippet.description: Battle Chef Brigade Deluxe, introducing Chef Ziggy and a smorgasbord of extra modes that test your cooking prowess, is coming to PlayStation 4, Switch, and Steam on August 28, 2018. Sharpen your knives and prepare for the ultimate cooking competition!
